2014-20-03  Enrico M. Crisostomo  <enrico.m.crisostomo@gmail.com>

        release: stable release 2

        * ax_cxx_have_bad_function_call.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_bind.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_bit_and.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_bit_or.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_bit_xor.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_cref.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_function.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_hash.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_is_bind_expression.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_is_placeholder.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_mem_fn.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_ref.m4: remove useless dependency.
	* ax_cxx_have_reference_wrapper.m4: remove useless dependency.

        release: stable release 1

        * ax_cxx_have_placeholders.m4: add new macro to check for
          std::placeholders.

